1341234317010034.Text: You know, of course, of Queen Barenziah. We returned to Mournhold together, after the unpleasantness in Wayrest. An amazing woman, our mother. Not one to be taken lightly. Not much happens in Mournhold that she is not aware of. She is a valuable asset to us.

1690013298249385562.Text: I suppose that is my official title. It means little to me. I have been a queen twice over now, and I have no wish to be involved in any of the intrigue. Still, it seems to bring joy to the people of Mournhold when they see the processions and the ceremonies. For that, I suppose, it is all worth it.

7797283132509821366.Text: Oh! The Lady Barenziah! A wonderful person. She's quite an interesting story, don't you think?

12426152572333921237.Text: You've spoken with her, and she said to speak with me? She's a wonderful person, and has become a great friend of mine over the years.
